des:
SHARP Life allows you to control compatible devices with Alexa.
This makes controlling your smart home even simpler and more intuitive:
1. Download our “SHARP Life” app in app market, then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “SHARP Life” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “SHARP Life” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on the plug.
Alexa, turn off the plug.

For more information, visit www.sharpconsumer.eu.
